Subject: drm/nouveau: Convert to platform remove callback returning void
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 0fa2db3bc7498d7b88e6742571cb832f749d625f
